headline: Is It Too Late To Consider General Electric (GE) After Its Strong Multi Year Rally
summary: If you are wondering whether General Electric is still reasonably priced after its long run, you are not alone. The question now is what the current share price actually implies about future expectations. The stock closed at US$293.87, with a 7 day return of a 9.6% decline and a 30 day return of a 6.7% decline. However, the 1 year return of 50.2% and 3 year return of about 3.5x show how strong the longer term move has been. Recent coverage has focused on General Electric's transformation...
